Custom Theme Attribution
========================

This custom theme is based on mkdocs-windmill-dark by Alexandre ZANNI (noraj).
Original repository: https://github.com/noraj1337/mkdocs-windmill-dark

mkdocs-windmill-dark is itself based on mkdocs-windmill by Grist Labs.
Original repository: https://github.com/gristlabs/mkdocs-windmill

Both original projects are licensed under the MIT License.

